<view class="tab-page">
  <view class="tab-hero">
    <view class="tab-hero__eyebrow">{{hero.eyebrow}}</view>
    <view class="tab-hero__title">{{hero.title}}</view>
    <view class="tab-hero__text">{{hero.text}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="overview-grid">
    <view class="overview-card" wx:for="{{overviewList}}" wx:key="label">
      <view class="overview-card__label">{{item.label}}</view>
      <view class="overview-card__value">{{item.value}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-block">
    <view class="section-block__title">课程亮点</view>
    <view class="section-block__text">这一版内容先承担页面占位和信息结构展示，后续可以直接替换成真实课程。</view>

    <view class="highlight-list">
      <view class="highlight-card" wx:for="{{highlightList}}" wx:key="title">
        <view class="highlight-card__title">{{item.title}}</view>
        <view class="highlight-card__text">{{item.text}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-block">
    <view class="section-block__title">培训模块</view>
    <view class="section-block__text">按“认知建立 -> 原型搭建 -> 协作实战 -> 上线交付”的顺序组织。</view>

    <view class="card-grid">
      <view class="academy-card" wx:for="{{moduleList}}" wx:key="id">
        <view class="academy-card__topline">
          <view class="academy-card__label">{{item.phase}}</view>
          <view class="academy-card__duration">{{item.duration}}</view>
        </view>
        <view class="academy-card__title">{{item.title}}</view>
        <view class="academy-card__text">{{item.description}}</view>

        <view class="lesson-tag-list">
          <view
            class="lesson-tag"
            wx:for="{{item.lessonList}}"
            wx:for-item="lesson"
            wx:key="*this"
          >
            {{lesson}}
          </view>
        </view>

        <view class="academy-card__deliverable">模块产出：{{item.deliverable}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-block">
    <view class="section-block__title">学完可得到</view>
    <view class="section-block__text">页面底部展示最终学习成果，也方便后续接入报名页或课程详情页。</view>

    <view class="outcome-list">
      <view class="outcome-card" wx:for="{{outcomeList}}" wx:key="title">
        <view class="outcome-card__title">{{item.title}}</view>
        <view class="outcome-card__text">{{item.text}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
